Ayrni iga yan wanaw n [[Tuga]] ittyawssan bahra g t[[Tafriqt n ugafa|friqt n ugafa]], acku [[imaziɣn]] iqqbuṛn ar sgis ssufuɣn kigan n twwuriwin izdin s [[Asafar|usafar]], [[Amttcu|umttcu]]. Ayrni iga yat tuga ittmɣin g wannaẓ n tafsut g tmizar g llant taganin nɣ igan zund taganin, ar iskar ifrawn izgzawn, iẓuṛan ns gan tagllatt irwasn [[aẓalim]] <ref>https://siyahatech18.blogspot.com/2015/04/eyerni-eguerni.html</ref>.

